{
  "sentences": [
    {
      "paraIndex": 0,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "诸葛亮和鲁肃坐船来到江东，想和孙权一方商量合作。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p1_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 0,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "厅里坐着许多学者，大家都关心百姓安定，也有不同想法。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p1_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 0,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "有人担心力量不够，有人担心路太难走。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p1_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 1,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "诸葛亮没有急着反驳。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p2_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 1,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "他先认真听完每个人的问题，再用简单的话回答。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p2_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 1,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "他说，遇到大事，只看害怕的一面，就会忘记还能互相帮助；",
      "audioPath": "audio/p2_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 1,
      "sentIndex": 3,
      "text": "只看自己的难处，也会看不见朋友的力量。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p2_s4.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 2,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "一位学者问，合作真的有用吗？",
      "audioPath": "audio/p3_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 2,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "诸葛亮说，江水很宽，一条船过江会摇晃，许多船按顺序前进就稳得多。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p3_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 2,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "人也是一样，分工清楚、彼此守信，就能把难题分成小步。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p3_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 3,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "另一个人问，怎样让百姓安心？",
      "audioPath": "audio/p4_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 3,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "诸葛亮回答，先把话说明白，再把事情安排好，不让大家空等。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p4_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 3,
      "sentIndex": 2,
      "text": "他的语气一直平和，既不取笑别人，也不夸耀自己，只把道理讲得清清楚楚。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p4_s3.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 4,
      "sentIndex": 0,
      "text": "听到后来，许多人点头，孙权也更愿意认真考虑合作。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p5_s1.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    },
    {
      "paraIndex": 4,
      "sentIndex": 1,
      "text": "这个故事告诉我们，会说话不是为了赢过别人，而是用礼貌和事实帮助大家看见好主意。",
      "audioPath": "audio/p5_s2.wav",
      "durationMs": 0,
      "unavailable": true
    }
  ]
}
